      "text": "# Baloney detection kit\n\nThe [[Baloney Detection Kit]] is a set of tools for skeptical thinking that [[Karl Sagan]] lays out in his book [[The Demon-Haunted World]]. It's a [[Bullshit Detector]]."
    },
