      "text": "[[Karl Sagan]] presents a set of tools for skeptical thinking which he calls the \"baloney detection kit\". Skeptical thinking consists both of constructing a reasoned argument and recognizing a fallacious ([[fallacy]]) or [[fraudulent]] one. "
